Context:
George Brown College is committed to ensuring accessibility for visits, tours, and events. Contact the event organizer for details and additional support by emailing aoda@georgebrown.ca. For directions, floor plans, and accessibility features, review the information provided. Learn about land acknowledgment and sign up for application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more. Reach out via phone at 416-415-2000 or TTY: 1-877-515-5559, or contact ask.george@georgebrown.ca. Visit the social media hub. Note: Information on this website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.

Contact Emails: aoda@georgebrown.ca, ask.george@georgebrown.ca
